# Documentation sync

| Change | Update |
|--------|--------|
| New endpoint | `docs/API_REFERENCE.md` |
| New flow | `docs/FLOWS.md` |
| Architecture change | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` |
| New component pattern | `docs/FRONTEND_GUIDE.md` |
| Schema change | `docs/ERD.md` |
| Deploy/env change | `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` |

Keep docs beginner-friendly. Use mermaid for non-trivial flows.
